<h2 id="preview-list-1">Preview list</h2>

<p>A preview list is a way to signpost users to other content using a link and short excerpt of text.</p>

<p>Preview lists should be used on higher level pages, such as the homepage and topic pages to signpost to:</p>
<ul>
  <li>service areas</li>
  <li>policies and legislation</li>
  <li>documents</li>
</ul>
